OL,4,C'reduced' due to staff relationships
OL,5,Cbreakdown
OL,7,FAs the Belfast Trust continues to try
OL,8,Fto resolve tensions within its cardiac
OL,9,Fsurgery unit, UTV can reveal that
OL,10,Fconflict within another medical team
OL,11,Fhad a serious impact on the delivery
OL,12,Fof some paediatric services within the
OL,13,FChildren's Hospital in 2024.
OL,15,FA mediation team had to be brought in
OL,16,Fwhen relationships amongst some staff
OL,17,Fwithin the paediatric gastroenterology
OL,18,Fteam broke down, "creating a risk to
OL,19,Fthe service's sustainability and
OL,20,Freduction in services."
