OL,7,FLast week, the Department of Health
OL,8,Fissued a number of recommendations for
OL,9,Fthe Belfast Trust to help resolve
OL,10,Fissues of conflict, bullying and poor
OL,11,Fbehaviour.
OL,13,FThe Health Minister says he is hoping
OL,14,Fto be able to lift some of the
OL,15,Foversight measures imposed on the
OL,16,FTrust in June "sooner rather than
OL,17,Flater."
