OL,7,FThe Belfast Trust is trying to rebuild
OL,8,Fthe confidence of staff, patients and
OL,9,Fthe public - confidence that was badly
OL,10,Fdamaged by a culture of bullying,
OL,11,Fconflict and toxic behaviour.
OL,13,FThe Department of Health imposed the
OL,14,Fhighest level of departmental
OL,15,Fintervention on the Belfast Trust in
OL,16,FJune, when the findings of a damning
OL,17,Freview into bullying and poor
OL,18,Fbehaviour amongst some surgeons within
OL,19,Fthe cardiac surgery unit at the Royal
OL,20,FVictoria Hospital, was made public by
OL,21,FUTV.
