OL,7,FWe can now reveal that concerns about
OL,8,Fthe impact poor relations amongst some
OL,9,Fteam members was having on the service
OL,10,Fwere flagged up with the Public Health
OL,11,FAgency, the Belfast Trust's Medical
OL,12,FDirector's Office and the department's
OL,13,Fpermanent secretary several months
OL,14,Fbefore in a cardiac surgery risk
OL,15,Fregister.
OL,17,FThe Belfast Trust document dated 19th
OL,18,FFebruary 2025, warned of a "risk to
OL,19,Fthe delivery of the full range of
OL,20,Fcardiac surgical services".
