OL,7,FThe register obtained under Freedom of
OL,8,FInformation, said this was "due to the
OL,9,Funexpected unavailability of a number
OL,10,Fof cardiac surgeons and acute
OL,11,Finterpersonal relationship issues
OL,12,Fwhich were affecting the daily
OL,13,Fdelivery of service".
OL,15,FHowever, the cardiac surgery service
OL,16,Fwas not the only area of the Trust to
OL,17,Fbe impacted by team conflict.
OL,19,FAnother risk register, this time for
OL,20,FChild Health, was drawn up in March
OL,21,F2024.
