OL,7,FIt warned that the paediatric
OL,8,Fgastroenterology team in the
OL,9,FChildren's Hospital was facing
OL,10,F"significant workforce pressures
OL,11,Frelated to team conflict and staff
OL,12,Fshortages" and that had "created a
OL,13,Frisk to the service's sustainability
OL,14,Fand a reduction in the services
OL,15,Favailable."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the Belfast Trust
OL,18,Fsaid no further issues related to
OL,19,Fconflcit in that team were documented
OL,20,Fin the first 6 months of 2025.
