OL,7,FThe Belfast Trust's new chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Jennifer Welsh has vowed to
OL,9,Fact immediately "to build a workplace
OL,10,Fthat is a safe and supportive
OL,11,Fenvironment for all."
OL,13,FIn a statement, she said: "The
OL,14,Frecommendations from the McBride/Hill
OL,15,Freport are a further and important
OL,16,Fnext step in responding to the support
OL,17,Fand interventions from Minister
OL,18,FNesbitt."
