OL,7,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt said:
OL,8,F"Patients deserve to be treated with
OL,9,Fcompassion, civility and with
OL,10,Fprofessionalism. By and large that
OL,11,Fhappens on a daily basis across health
OL,12,Fand social care but where it doesn't
OL,13,Fhappen, it is my duty to make sure the
OL,14,Fright interventions are put in place."
OL,16,FMr Nesbitt is hoping to be in a
OL,17,Fposition to soon downgrade the current
OL,18,Foversight measures but that will
OL,19,Fdepend on how quickly the Trust can
OL,20,Fbegin to repair relationships.
